{"type": "article", "id": 33043, "title": "加拿大鹅准备IPO，以及，Supreme 与 Levi’s 合作 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-09T02:55:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4278, "name": "Interbrand"}, {"id": 33701, "name": "最有价值百大品牌"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 5171, "name": "Canada Goose"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 20048, "name": "Nordstrom"}, {"id": 33702, "name": "London Undercover"}, {"id": 3264, "name": "山本耀司"}, {"id": 33703, "name": "权志龙"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161009101619McxbUYjuWSEf0pkJ.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/ralph-lauren-promotes-founders-son-to-help-make-brand-hip-again\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 起用创始人的儿子为副总裁</b></a> | 在Ralph Lauren 创立近 50 年之际，Ralph Lauren 的儿子 David Lauren 被品牌任命为新的副总裁，将带领品牌革新，更新品牌形象并实现业绩增长。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/forecasts-analysis/apple-google-coca-cola-top-interbrands-2016-ranking-10655283/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Interbrand 公布 2016 年度全球最有价值百大品牌，LV 位列奢侈品牌第一</b></a> | 广告巨头 Omnicom 旗下的品牌咨询机构 Interbrand 发布 2016 全球最有价值百大品牌榜单。共有八个奢侈品牌上榜，品牌总价值为 755 亿美元。其中，LV、Hermès、Gucci 分别位列前三。Dior 首次上榜，排名 89。去年位列 96 的 Hugo Boss 跌出了榜单。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/canada-goose-preparing-for-ipo-1475869376\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Canada Goose 正在筹备 IPO</b></a> | 据《华尔街日报》消息称，加拿大轻奢羽绒服品牌 Canada Goose 正在筹备 IPO，若进展顺利，或将于明年年初正式公开募股，该公司的最高估值可达到 20 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/nordstrom-just-says-no-to-moschino-capsule-10658503/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Moschino 的药丸系列引争议，Nordstrom 下架了该系列</b></a> | Jeremy Scott 为 Moschino 设计的药丸系列引起了不小的争议，被指有美化药物成瘾的嫌疑。美国高档百货连锁店 Nordstrom 下架了 Moschino 这个系列在其网店及三个门店销售的产品。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009101257tSPERgJGwhBTWvd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的： </h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/g-dragon-peaceminusone\" rel=\"nofollow\">G-Dragon 正式推出个人品牌 PEACEMINUSONE</a>。这个品牌是 G-Dragon 将不同范畴的创意理念融入时尚的一项企划，该系列由艺术家、G-Dragon 的造型师 GeeEun 设计，打造了包括帽款、T-Shirt 等一系列单品。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016100909551185ICuTgiMzSHx9QO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095521fkIZhXglHQGSP4Y0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095530ykJqUAdfbiwY5ELV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095530riOfamq2Ij9pVLPz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/supreme-x-levis-2016-fall-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supreme 与 Levi’s 合作，推出 2016 秋季全新联名系列</a>。该系列以 Levi’s 招牌的 Trucker Jacket 和 501 Jeans 作为蓝本，并在夹克中加入了羊羔绒内里来提高保暖性。这个联名系列将于 10 月 6 日登陆纽约、伦敦、巴黎旗舰店和线上店铺。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095633Yer3ckKLoJOA246B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095633PiaERtUZxdHqSJhn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095647zM8yvkfpP5mBx7KA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095647SIOwngdR40yJ29vF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095648ksJ2GKyTBpFNXnoW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095648MRnyEOlIvV8WStK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095656a4iVseJBMpUIRbxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610090956561rJ2WgbHLy8fYCwa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/vans-vault-x-london-undercover-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vault by Vans 与 London Undercover 跨界合作</a>，携手带来多个联名鞋款和雨伞。Vault by Vans 把雨伞设计中的印花图案和迷彩运用到了鞋身设计上，并搭载加厚鞋底以增加户外技能感。这个系列将于 10 月 24 日起在品牌的指定店铺发售，每双鞋的定价均为 130 英镑。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095708s8MyFpDLOniVHYWU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095717Dp41nUQEBNlCvJ2h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095717TGnULZFP2WOjJEd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095726PrsNuL94qGcegXY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/wisdom-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">台湾时装品牌 wisdom 发布了它的 2017 春夏系列</a>，wisdom 以都市户外为主打，又不乏时尚元素。这个新的系列以 UNRESOLVABLE 为主题，以白、灰、蓝等冷调性色系为主色调，打造出造型多样富于变化的款式设计。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095739vAYEBCn6T29edHRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095739s5Y1hXQo8zdwHxgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740Vq584sohk3EcCXbD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740xWzsMZTSpFP5X1Jg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740Kq2afepMnBExXz7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610090957401rILfXQips5NHS2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740cDioOduVkm406PG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740YexkPI3Svbc5RdOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740UNbWhKHZ7ClLGOcx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095740MNoJ8pSKiDWB3lCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610090957418FVK5ksyxog9ANQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095741F7TD2IOSe3zwvBZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095754hNpZaYisHtoxRvK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095754YvmC4G67nek0ZM5I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/yohji-yamamoto-x-adidas-2016-fw-boots\" rel=\"nofollow\">山本耀司与 adidas 再度合作</a>，带来了两双全新联名靴款。在全黑色调的贯穿下，显露硬朗与独特的暗黑气质。该鞋款定价分别为 60000 和 64000 日元，目前已在山本耀司 Yohji Yamamoto 全球各大指定店铺上架。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161009095812JfWHlqOMG9Yrz478.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610090958037tGrXDVEhOMwKzFQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}